&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Covid Screening Service &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are seeking to recruit experienced Administration Assistant to join the Covid-19 Screening team located at Queen Alexandra Hospital in Portsmouth on a fixed term basis. This is a newly established team that facilitates the Covid screening for both staff via a drive through service, and pre elective patient appointments, working under the direction of the RN Covid Coordinator. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The service is a flexible and responsive provision, currently open 7 days a week, 365 days a year. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be required to work from 07:30 to 14:00, 4 days a week, supporting both the pre elective patient pathway and symptomatic staff pathway. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You must have a good level of experience working in an administrative environment and must also be computer literate. Previous NHS experience and knowledge of hospital systems (PAS) would be an advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be someone who works well in a team and is able to communicate effectively with staff and members of the public. Within the team, you will be able to priorities your work in order to meet clinic deadlines, be comfortable using your initiative and work independently when required. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Your primary responsibilities will be:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To ensure timely appointments are booked within the clinical guidelines&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To ensure the clinics run service runs efficiently&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use of computerised systems including Patient Administration System&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;General admin tasks to support the service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Be flexible to cross cover annual leave when required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note due the large number of applicants, we cannot directly contact you if your application is unsuccessful.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing Date 18/11/2020&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
